'''Horoh''' was a [[Killik/Legends|Killik]] hive that existed during the [[Cold War (Galactic Republic–Sith Empire)|Cold War]], and survived the [[Swarm War]] over four thousand years later. In [[44 ABY]] Horoh was selling their [[Membrosia/Legends|membrosia]] products to [[Restaurant Galatina]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]].

